## Limitations

The findings are based on hypothetical scenarios and user-generated content, which may not fully capture the complexities of political systems. The perspectives gathered are subjective and may not represent a comprehensive analysis of the potential impacts of a world without democracy. Additionally, the sources used are not peer-reviewed, which may affect the reliability of the information.

